        private Dictionary<string, string> GetGroupCodes()
        {
            var output = new Dictionary<string, string>();
            /***Get viewState**/
            _httpWebRequest =
                (HttpWebRequest) WebRequest.Create("http://www.waytoumrah.com/prj_umrah/Eng/Eng_frmMofaRtp.aspx");
            _httpWebRequest.Method = "GET";
            _httpWebRequest.Host = Host;
            _httpWebRequest.CookieContainer = _cookieContainer;

            _httpWebReponse = (HttpWebResponse) _httpWebRequest.GetResponse();
            var responseStream = _httpWebReponse.GetResponseStream();

            if (responseStream == null) return output;
            var responseReader = new StreamReader(responseStream);
            var responseHtml = responseReader.ReadToEnd();
            responseReader.Close();
            responseStream.Close();

            var doc = new HtmlDocument();
            doc.LoadHtml(responseHtml);
            GetViews(responseHtml);
            var cmbGroupcodes = doc.DocumentNode.SelectSingleNode("//select[@name='cmbGroupcodes']");

            if (cmbGroupcodes == null)
            {
                output.Add("-1",
                    "Group Error: You don't seem to have a permission to view the MOFA pages using your current username and password ");
                return output;
            }
            try
            {
                foreach (var input in cmbGroupcodes.SelectNodes(".//option"))
                {
                    var outerhtml = input.OuterHtml;
                    var groupCode = Regex.Match(outerhtml, "value=\"(\\d+)\"");
                    if (groupCode.Success)
                    {
                        var code = groupCode.Groups[1].ToString();
                        if (code == "0") continue;
                        var groupName = Regex.Match(responseHtml, outerhtml + "(.+)</option");
                        if (groupName.Success)
                        {
                            output.Add(code, Regex.Replace(groupName.Groups[1].ToString(), @"\s\s+", " "));
                        }
                    }
                }

                var cmbUoNode = doc.DocumentNode.SelectSingleNode("//select[@name='cmbUo']");
                foreach (var input in cmbUoNode.SelectNodes(".//option"))
                {
                    var outerhtml = input.OuterHtml;
                    var groupCode = Regex.Match(outerhtml, "value=\"(\\d+)\"");
                    if (groupCode.Success)
                    {
                        //Umrah operator mokhaa association and link to the company
                        //var uoName =
                        //    cmbUoNode.InnerHtml.Split('-')[1].Replace("\t", string.Empty)
                        //        .Replace("\n", string.Empty)
                        //        .Replace("\r", string.Empty);
                        //_dal.UpdateSaudiWakeelId(CompanyId, "W", uoName);                        
                        var code = groupCode.Groups[1].ToString();
                        if (code == "0") continue;
                        _cmbUo = code;
                    }
                }
                var cmbEaNode = doc.DocumentNode.SelectSingleNode("//select[@name='cmbEa']");
                foreach (var input in cmbEaNode.SelectNodes(".//option"))
                {
                    var outerhtml = input.OuterHtml;
                    var groupCode = Regex.Match(outerhtml, "value=\"(\\d+)\"");
                    if (groupCode.Success)
                    {
                        var code = groupCode.Groups[1].ToString();
                        if (code == "0") continue;
                        _cmbEa = code;
                    }
                }
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                output.Add("-1", "Group Error " + ex.Message);
            }


            return output;
        }

            {
                stream.Write(postDataBytes, 0, postDataBytes.Length);
            }

            var responseStream = _httpWebReponse.GetResponseStream();

            {
                var responseReader = new StreamReader(responseStream);
                var responseHtml = responseReader.ReadToEnd();

                if (responseHtml == "0|error|500||")
                    return "Error:" + responseHtml;

                responseReader.Close();
                responseStream.Close();
                var doc = new HtmlDocument();
                doc.LoadHtml(responseHtml);
                var table = doc.DocumentNode.SelectSingleNode("//table[@id='dgrdMofaRpt']");
                if (table == null)
                {
                    return "Error: Can't find dgrdMofaRpt" + responseHtml;
                }
                var rows = table.Descendants("tr");
                foreach (var row in rows)
                {
                    var columns =
                        row.SelectNodes("th|td");
                    if (columns.Count > 9)
                    {
                        var passportNumber = columns[
                            5].
                            InnerText.Trim();
                        if (passportNumber == "&nbsp;") continue;
                        var mofaNumber = columns[6].InnerText.Trim();

                        var embassy = columns[8].InnerText.Trim();
                        output += passportNumber + "," + mofaNumber + "," + embassy + "\n";
                    }
                }

                if (responseHtml.Contains("dgrdMofaRpt$ctl104$ctl01")) //get the second page
                    output = output + GetCsvContents2(inputGroupCode);
            }

            return output;
        }


        private string EscapeUriString(string input)
        {
            var limit = 2000;

            var sb = new StringBuilder();
            var loops = input.Length/limit;

            for (var i = 0; i <= loops; i++)
            {
                sb.Append(i < loops
                    ? Uri.EscapeDataString(input.Substring(limit * i, limit))
                    : Uri.EscapeDataString(input.Substring(limit * i)));
            }

            return sb.ToString();
        }

        [DllImport("wininet.dll", SetLastError = true)]
        private static extern bool InternetGetCookieEx(string pchURL, string pchCookieName,
                       StringBuilder pchCookieData, ref System.UInt32 pcchCookieData,
                       int dwFlags, IntPtr lpReserved);
        private static int INTERNET_COOKIE_HTTPONLY = 0x00002000;
        public static CookieContainer GetAspCookie(string host)
        {
            var output = new CookieContainer();



            StringBuilder cookie = new StringBuilder();
            uint size = 256;
            InternetGetCookieEx("https://www.waytoumrah.com", "ASP.NET_SessionId", cookie, ref size,
                INTERNET_COOKIE_HTTPONLY, IntPtr.Zero);
            var coockieValue = cookie.Replace("ASP.NET_SessionId=", string.Empty);
            output.Add(new Cookie("ASP.NET_SessionId", coockieValue.ToString(), "", ".www.waytoumrah.com"));
            cookie = new StringBuilder();
            return output;
        }

        private Dictionary<string,string> GetDomControlElements(string html , List<string> inputElements)
        {
            var output = new Dictionary<string,string>();
            var doc = new HtmlDocument();
            doc.LoadHtml(html);

            GetDomControlElement(doc, output, "__VIEWSTATE");
            GetDomControlElement(doc, output, "__VIEWSTATEGENERATOR");
            GetDomControlElement(doc, output, "__EVENTVALIDATION");
            foreach (var inputElement in inputElements)
            {
                GetDomControlElement(doc, output, inputElement);
            }
            return output;
        }

        private void GetDomControlElement(HtmlDocument doc, Dictionary<string, string> controlsDictionary, string controlItem)
        {
            var vsNode = doc.GetElementbyId("__VIEWSTATE");
            if (vsNode != null && vsNode.HasAttributes && vsNode.Attributes["value"] != null)
            {
                if (controlsDictionary.Keys.Contains(controlItem))
                    controlsDictionary[controlItem] =  EscapeUriString(vsNode.Attributes["value"].Value);
                else
                    controlsDictionary.Add(controlItem, EscapeUriString(vsNode.Attributes["value"].Value));
            }
            else //Try to parse the html for 
            {
                var regViewState = Regex.Match(doc.ToString(), @"__VIEWSTATE" + Regex.Escape("|") + "(.+?)" + Regex.Escape("|"));
                if (regViewState.Success)
                {
				if (controlsDictionary.Keys.Contains(controlItem))
				    controlsDictionary[controlItem] =  EscapeUriString(regViewState.Groups[1].ToString());
                    else
                    controlsDictionary.Add(controlItem, EscapeUriString(regViewState.Groups[1].ToString()));
                }
            }
        }
